releases.body:
Initial _test builds_ of basic `safe:` browser. 

Will route `safe://` urls to the SAFE Network launcher.

This is only tested on OSX so far, so the state of these releases is unknown. 

Both windows and linux are untested, so please let me know if/when you run into trouble!
